platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Fall in love with a new book

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Inspired by the timeless story of a little egg on a leaf, Hungry Caterpillar Play School is as sweet and colorful as Eric Carle’s beloved children’s book. The app is all about play and exploration; kids can draw, color, sing, and even learn to grow strawberries (for the caterpillar’s snack).
